# Project Context: all-in-one-frontend

## Code language

- **Generated code is always in English**, never in Portuguese: variable names, function names, comments, strings in the UI, log messages, and any other code or copy produced by the AI must be written in English, even when the user's instructions are in Portuguese.

## Stack

- **Framework**: Vue 3 (Composition API) + TypeScript
- **Build**: Vite 7
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4, CSS variables (slate base), tw-animate-css
- **UI**: shadcn-vue (New York style), Reka UI, Lucide icons
- **State**: Pinia
- **Routing**: Vue Router 4
- **HTTP**: Axios (client in `src/core/api/client.ts`; interceptor returns `response.data` and normalizes errors with `message`)

## Main structure (MVC Modular)

- `src/core/` — shared infrastructure: `api/client.ts`, `lib/` (utils, format), `composables/useTheme`, `router/`, `stores/counter`
- `src/shared/` — shared UI: `components/ui/` (shadcn), `components/AppSidebar.vue`, `layouts/AuthenticatedLayout.vue`
- `src/modules/<module>/` — feature modules; each has `model/` (api, store) and `view/` (Vue pages)
  - `auth` — model: api, store; view: LoginView, RegisterView
  - `dashboard` — view: DashboardView
  - `accounts-payable` — model: api, users; view: AccountsPayableView
- `src/assets/index.css` — global styles and theme

## Aliases (`@/`)

- `@/core/*`, `@/shared/*`, `@/modules/*` (tsconfig); components.json: `@/shared/components`, `@/core/lib`, `@/core/composables`

## Conventions

- Vue components in PascalCase; composables with `use` prefix
- Auth: `useAuthStore` from `@/modules/auth/model/store` (token in localStorage); public vs protected routes via `meta.requiresAuth` and `meta.public`
- Theme: initialized in `main.ts` via `initTheme()` from `@/core/composables/useTheme`
- New UI components: use shadcn-vue (components.json) when it makes sense
- Env: `VITE_API_URL` for the API (see `env.d.ts` and `.env.example`)

## Scripts

- `pnpm dev` — development
- `pnpm build` — type-check + build
- `pnpm lint` — ESLint with fix
- `pnpm format` — Prettier on `src/`
